  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK736">
<l>kēṭaṟiyāk keṭṭa viṭattum vaḷaṅkuṉṟā</l>
<l>nāṭeṉpa nāṭṭiṟ ṟalai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learned say that the best kingdom is that which knows no evil (from its foes), and, if injured (at all), suffers no diminution in its fruitfulness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
